[3]
Date: Mon 9 Nov 2020
From: EpiCore Global Surveillance Project member [edited]


It was tagged strange disease of unknown origin affecting and killing people in the communities in Delta State, in the South South geopolitical zones of the country, Nigeria. Symptoms include high grade fever, general body weakness, malaise, vomiting, bleeding. Yellowness of the eyes, and the body were not major signs seen. Samples where taken from affected people and sent to the National Reference Laboratory, Nigeria, and it was confirmed to be highly positive for yellow fever.

